legacy.full_text:

1.jointly developing a right perception.
2.jointly managing disagreements effectively. 
3.jointly advancing mutually beneficial coop. 
4.jointly shouldering responsibilities as major countries. 
5.jointly promoting people-to-people exchanges. https://t.co/TkrMRuW2oM
